    "long_instructions": "#### Layering Beats \r\n\r\nYour friend, Caroline, needs help layering beats with the sounds she was given. Create a  10-measure backbeat that uses at least one rest and one sound effect. \r\n\r\nChallenge: Try to recreate this timline that plays one sound, then overlaps the same sound before it's done.\r\n\r\n![](https://images.code.org/fa037d7a27293c030e8b80f03c3da413-image-1741727610707.13.00 PM.png)",
